dcterms:description: The CelebA dataset is a large-scale face attributes dataset collected by Liu et al. It consists of over 200,000 facial images of celebrities, each annotated with 40 binary attribute labels, including attributes such as gender appearance, perceived age, hair color, and facial expressions. The images in the dataset are diverse, featuring celebrities from various ethnicities, ages, and backgrounds.
dcterms:title: CelebA
